This folder contains scripts that are useful for restarting simulations

autostarter.pl
  -- Perl script that can automatically restart simulations.
  -- A simple restart input file is required for the script.
  -- The directory 'modules' is a required dependency for this script

make_visit_file.py
  -- Python script that can regenerate the visit_dumps and lag_dumps file.
  -- Useful if you need all files written to the visit_dumps or lag_dumps file.

regen_viz_input_files.pl
  -- Perl script that regenerates all visualization files.
  -- Useful if the files are written out at consistent time intervals.
